{"title": "NP-Completeness", "body": {"ops": [{"attributes": {"color": "#47a1b3", "underline": true}, "insert": "NP-Completeness"}, {"attributes": {"header": 2}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "Some problems are "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#47a1b3"}, "insert": "harder "}, {"insert": "than others - if they were all easy then we wouldn't be here studying this (and what a blessed world that would be). So we would like a way to think about a way to quantify the "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#47a1b3"}, "insert": "hardness "}, {"insert": "of a problem. "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#47a1b3"}, "insert": "NP-Completeness"}, {"insert": " gives us a framework to consider this.\n\nFormally, a problem "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#98add9"}, "insert": "A"}, {"insert": " is "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#47a1b3"}, "insert": "NP-complete"}, {"insert": " "}, {"attributes": {"italic": true}, "insert": "iff"}, {"insert": ":\n\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#98add9"}, "insert": "A"}, {"insert": " is "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#47a1b3"}, "insert": "NP-hard"}, {"insert": ", and"}, {"attributes": {"list": "ordered"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"attributes": {"color": "#98add9"}, "insert": "A"}, {"insert": " is in "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#50c75a"}, "insert": "NP"}, {"insert": "."}, {"attributes": {"list": "ordered"}, "insert": "\n"}]}, "text": "NP-Completeness\n\nSome problems are harder than others - if they were all easy then we wouldn't be here studying this (and what a blessed world that would be). So we would like a way to think about a way to quantify the hardness of a problem. NP-Completeness gives us a framework to consider this.\n\n\n\n\nFormally, a problem A is NP-complete iff:\n\n\n\n\nA is NP-hard, and\nA is in NP.", "updatedAt": 1714594740015}